title: Precision at Your Fingertips with Bosch Induction Cooktops
description: Life can feel rushed – that’s why Bosch induction cooktops are designed to speed up dinner, making cooking faster and more efficient. With PowerMove’s pre-set heat levels simply slide your pan across the zones to quickly change the heat level. When dinner slows down, life can slow down. Learn more here: http://www.bosch-home.com/us/productslist/cooking-baking/cooktops/induction-cooktops.
